{"tid":1438201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭記招篩選傳媒  經濟問題優先  我覺得記者可以咁","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:03:52.000Z","uid":221265,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"010a6e6cbf983cbb9e25a2c20d2536687ad7d395","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"林鄭及各政府 警察記招都越嚟越玩依招<br />\n<br />\n就咁叫記者杯葛行唔通<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋嘅專業係唔會唔去記招嘅<br />\n但我覺得可以咁：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者去到，一致唔理佢嘅點名程序<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n帶個咪狂問問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目的係唔俾佢按佢嘅規則做show<br />\n點名問啲no harm甚或助佢攻嘅問題！<br />\n<br />\n最好攪到佢個問題環節腰斬！<br />\n<br />\n記者可在現場抗議<br />\n<br />\n想現役記者入嚟講下有無其他招！"},{"pid":"4863c2ffcd0ae354cb1511d150a6df95c337b70d","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8060xp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8060xp6.jpg&h=4fa987ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日爆seed 狂鬧新聞處篩選傳媒嘅<br />\n係利君雅嘅同事，港台視點31主持彭德章"},{"pid":"3fea9d98221fc0d6bbbf7e7d743baec8f339cc71","tid":1438201,"uid":90236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f3c22958a69007ebdab8da0317b2f5865675f1b","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"依個問題絕對要正視"},{"pid":"e1f259874615bbe6ba452d007bc4a0f464095f49","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"港台，蘋果，立場<br />\n3間如果合作狂問問題<br />\n唔理佢嘅程序<br />\n<br />\n我覺得絕對有效<br />\n<br />\n其他記者當然都歡迎夾計<br />\n<br />\n大家睇住<br />\n<br />\n今日有得問問題嘅<br />\n全撚部都喺同林鄭政府夾埋<br />\n5條問題咁撚少<br />\n仲要點名垃圾中新社！"},{"pid":"6e213f4517ce3c2af40d996529bee424149d087b","tid":1438201,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"不如有個共識，比想屌柒777既幾個問先"},{"pid":"16846f86edcb203c150d718ea7be3f230bea9caa","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"6e213f4517ce3c2af40d996529bee424149d087b","tid":1438201,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"不如有個共識，比想屌柒777既幾個問先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"你錯啦<br />\n唔係記者決定邊個問先<br />\n<br />\n係有新聞官點名嘅<br />\n故記者都要逆權<br />\n反客為主<br />\n<br />\n盡量團結(當然好多紅媒唔會睬你)<br />\n一到QA 就狂問<br />\n唔理個新聞官<br />\n<br />\n仲要好似叫口號咁<br />\n話<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭你篩選問題 摧毀新聞自由<br />\n當記者政治宣傳工具！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n夠齊心，唔會疊聲<br />\n入晒咪<br />\n<br />\n就可embarrass佢！"},{"pid":"bc2125d4204a9c5f3659f1c2bc6360c0f2c9d825","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:16:19.000Z","msg":"推到有現役記者獻計"},{"pid":"724662a3d27b9e8bb860b4b50e4e093ec6faa6b8","tid":1438201,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"記者帶手提咪<br />\n只有有咪在手，就有主動既發言權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed66b214ec02685ab245be12cb2eff16fc7b1ef","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"724662a3d27b9e8bb860b4b50e4e093ec6faa6b8","tid":1438201,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"記者帶手提咪<br />\n只有有咪在手，就有主動既發言權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n當然要解決技術問題<br />\n會同咪stand個咪互干擾有wan wan聲㗎<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定要拉攏記者團結反佢<br />\n<br />\n得1,2個做無用<br />\n<br />\n太多仆街紅媒"},{"pid":"6ab0f34b70428aa09dc3617419f9f1e748a2ee61","tid":1438201,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"724662a3d27b9e8bb860b4b50e4e093ec6faa6b8","tid":1438201,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"記者